Package: circlizePlus
Title: Object-oriented Circular Visualization
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Tianze", "Cao", , "hnrcao.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4308-1878"))
Description: circlizePlus is a wrapper for circlize. All components are based on classes and objects. Users can use the addition symbol (+) to combine components for a circular visualization with ggplot2 style.
